        "Id": "91482976-def9-4cdd-8d1e-318033513a88",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The Elusive 5",
        "Location": "LOCATION_NORTHAMERICA",
        "PublicId": "122044621346",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/skunk/scene_skunk.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 70244617-fd54-4b9f-8412-fcdea02d91eb).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47. Your targets are known as the &quot;Elusive 5&quot;. Each are an elite member belonging to the Syndicate&apos;s top forces. Our efforts in the past to locate and eliminate the 5 have been unsuccessful until now.  Recent intel shows that they are posing as ordinary civilians in a quiet town called Whitteton Creek and are not staying long so time is of the essence. You must not alert anyone or we risk losing their trail. Proceed with caution 47.",
